ons","To ask the Secretary of State for the Home Department, pursuant to the Answer of 12 February 2019 to Question 218267, to which projects  (a) the €42.5 million has been committed and (b) the remainder of that funding will be committed.","false","Biography information for Charlie Elphicke","Dover","Charlie Elphicke","220876"
